{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were quite a lot because you weren't-- you had-- virtually had to stand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sort of-- so there must have been quite a few.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It seemed to me like a large space, but very, very little room in between.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I think more than that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would think maybe about 20 or 30 people used to hide in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of various ages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes we would stay there all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parent-- my father told me that what happened was that, he had some sort of contacts with people on the outside of the ghetto, and they knew approximately when the pogrom-- I suppose that's the word I should use-- was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had some sort of forewarning, because he always seemed to know when to hide and rush us down there, because apparently they just came in indiscriminately and would walk down the street, or walk into a house, and whoever was there was taken.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a quota system of taking x number of Jews or people, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't discriminate in the sense that they didn't have to look too hard to find them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if you had some forewarning you were able to, perhaps, hide and avoid the inevitable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, as I said I was told by my mother and warned about uttering a sound.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a form of-- how should I put it-- to scare me she told me the stories of other children that had been taken.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just a-- just a small bed next to my parents', in one small room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think we had very-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think we had very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's just the sort of clothes that we had and a few cooking utensils.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
